and on the seventh day god rested and thought to himself i am hungry for a steak so he made an old school steak house and he thought to himself all is well with the world don t listen to the haters BADREVIEW this place has a patina to it enjoy it in this world of chain restaurants order a steak cook it yourself and ask eddie for advice on how to spice it eddie has been there longer than some customers are old if you like an old school steakhouse this is a must this is on my top 10 for casual dining
